title: Classic New York Style Hot Dogs  with Fried Onions, Spiced Chips and 'Slaw
description: This Classic New York Style Hot Dogs is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
